title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 6 §§ 210-1.1 - Applicability
content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 6 §§ 210-1.1 - Applicability

State Regulations
(a) This Part
applies to all 2006 and subsequent model-year personal watercraft engines, unless otherwise indicated, offered for sale or lease, or sold, or leased, for
registration in this State. (b) The
provisions of this Part also apply to personal watercraft engines of the United

States or its agencies. Notes
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 6
§§
210-1.1

State regulations are updated quarterly; we currently have two versions available. Below is a
comparison between our most recent version and the prior quarterly release. More comparison features will be added as we have more versions to compare. No prior version found.
